videos.description: Reid Travis draws the double team and finds freshman Keldon Johnson on the perimeter for a 3-pointer vs. Utah.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Johnson nails wide-open 3-pointer

videos.description: Keldon Johnson gets the hot hand in the 1st half for Kentucky, draining 3-pointers on three consecutive possessions.
videos.headline: Johnson off to hot start vs. Utah

videos.description: PJ Washington steals the Utah inbounds pass and heads the other way for a one-handed slam in transition.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington skies for fast-break dunk
